==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Impeachable
<hw>Im*peach"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>That may be
impeached; liable to impeachment; chargeable with a crime.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Owners of lands in fee simple are not <qex>impeachable</qex> for
waste.</q> <rj><qau>Z. Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Impeacher</ent>⟦br⟧
